<!-- About Us Section -->
<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h2 class="section-heading">Who We Are</h2>
            <p class="section-subheading">HR Recruitment Solutions is a leading HR technology provider, offering businesses a modern, streamlined, and efficient online recruitment process. Our innovative platform helps companies connect with top talent effortlessly, while enhancing their hiring processes.</p>
            <p>Founded with the goal of simplifying recruitment, we leverage cutting-edge technology to bring automation, AI-powered candidate matching, and seamless collaboration tools to the forefront of recruitment. Whether you’re a small startup or a large enterprise, our system helps you identify the right candidates faster and more accurately.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h2 class="section-heading">Our Mission</h2>
            <p>To empower organizations with the tools and technology to simplify their hiring process, reduce time-to-hire, and ensure the best talent is matched with the right opportunities. We strive to make recruitment smarter, faster, and more inclusive.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

