            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card p-3">
                <h5 class="card-title">Seamless Collaboration Tools</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Collaboration made easy with our platform. Share candidate profiles, feedback, and progress with your team in real-time to make faster, more informed decisions.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
